status-checker-heading: (FR) What is the Dependent Status Checker?
status-checker-content: (FR) The Dependent Status Checker is a tool that lets you check the status of your dependent's Canadian Dental Care Plan application.
online-status-heading: (FR) Who can check their dependent's application status online?
online-status-content: (FR) If you applied for the Canadian Dental Care Plan for your dependent, you can check their status online.
